h1. The Apache Karaf Team posted on January 2, 2015\\Karaf 2.4.1 released!

The Karaf team is pleased to announce the availability of [Karaf 2.4.1|index/community/download/karaf-2.4.1-release.html].

This is an update patch for Apache Karaf 2.4.x, containing many bug fixes, dependency updates, and improvements. New features highlights include: Regex support in features commands, added an option to uninstall transitive features, and renamed jpa feature as jpa/jpa20 and jpa21.
For more information, please see the [release notes|index/community/download/karaf-2.4.1-release.html].
